text: Leah Clark (born December 20, 1979 in Albuquerque, New Mexico) is an American actress. She has provided many voices for Japanese anime series and video games. The roles she is most famous for are Coby in One Piece, Blair in Soul Eater, and Fuyuki in Sgt.
